data.description: Priced to sell! BEAUTIFUL, immaculate home! You cannot beat this view and large lot! This three year old home is gorgeous, on 3/4 an acre and boasts upgrades such as luxury vinyl plank flooring, granite kitchen countertops and whole house gutters. It has an extended patio on the rear of the house, perfect for relaxing in the large backyard. It has four bedrooms, two full bathrooms and an upgraded luxury master bath with separate tub and shower. Refrigerator, washer and dryer stay with the home! This gem won't last long - schedule your appointment today!
